Bash
--------------------
Windows: N/A
Linux  : To be added (you can always link the file with ln)

Vim
--------------------
Windows: Run install.bat in the vim directory
Linux  : Run install.sh in the vim directory

Support
--------------------
Installing the Monaco font
  Windows:
    Right click support/fonts/Monaco.ttf -> Install
  Linux: (tested on ubuntu 10.04 and 10.10)
    Run install-fonts.sh in the support directory (as root)
